    public class FetchCustomObjectsGraphQlRequest
extends GraphQlBaseRequestImpl<ResourceKeyIdGraphQlResult>
    A SphereRequest implementation to allow SphereClient to execute graphQL queries on CTP. It provides a POST request to the CTP graphql API containing body to fetch custom object resource with the given container name defined in endpoint parameter.
